
### 2) `site/index.html`
```html
<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Simran • AWS Website CI/CD</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="./styles.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1> AWS Website CI/CD (S3 + CloudFront)</h1>
    <p>Deployed via GitHub Actions • IaC with Terraform</p>
  </header>
  <main>
    <section class="card">
      <h2>Welcome</h2>
      <p>This is a minimal static site scaffold to show end-to-end DevOps on AWS.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>S3 (private) + CloudFront (OAC)</li>
        <li>GitHub Actions: sync + invalidation</li>
        <li>SPA-friendly 404 → index.html</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <section class="grid">
      <div class="tile"><h3>Speed</h3><p>Global CDN via CloudFront.</p></div>
      <div class="tile"><h3>Security</h3><p>Bucket is private; only CloudFront can read.</p></div>
      <div class="tile"><h3>IaC</h3><p>Recreate infra with Terraform.</p></div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <footer>
    <p>© <span id="year"></span> Simran Singh — DevOps on AWS</p>
  </footer>
  <script>document.getElementById('year').textContent = new Date().getFullYear();</script>
</body>
</html>
